tedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:44:04.000Z","msg":"因多年來完全忘記了是誰大力支持，過橋抽板，亦沒有兌現服務香港市民的承諾，實在忘恩負義到極點的民建聯<br />\n<br />\n簡稱因聯"},{"pid":"1c8decf708b3b63c6cbd48f31abc3751c2842968","tid":1299580,"uid":266375,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:49:42.000Z","msg":"學者指民建聯做法荒唐，與政府皆如「縮頭烏龜」<br />\n<br />\n民建聯的表現就像逃兵，逃兵在古代是要被處死的<br />\n<br />\n即係政府都要處死?"},{"pid":"19b237ec9a102982c819886dd5323bea8b6f01de","tid":1299580,"uid":224602,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:50:02.000Z","msg":"第一 東方唔係香港第一大報<br />\n第二 佢插民建聯 我地係應該開心 因為鬼打鬼 <br />\n        東方都係支持垃圾港共一份子<br />\n第三 咁既垃圾報紙 只有廢老先會睇 <br />\n講完<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1532d9b9679bf2d4fdf7fdca37c7c85083d9125b","tid":1299580,"uid":161709,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:52:31.000Z","msg":"重申7大訴求：<br />\n1. 撤回送中惡法<br />\n2. 撤回暴動定義<br />\n3. 撤銷對抗爭者控罪<br />\n4. 追究黑警暴行，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n5. 落實真雙普選<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>承諾不推行社會信用評分制度</strong></span><br />\n7.<strong> <span style=\"color: red;\">拆除所有監控燈柱</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">試著說監控燈柱, 不要說智慧燈柱</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07010ad8f11f2385dccd79c829e8327f7115705a","tid":1299580,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1u6Lb70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1u6Lb70.png&h=84e8e474&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31a9082a63eb342c2003c894bce8f025b8b595d8","tid":1299580,"uid":154763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:06:12.000Z","msg":"係咪想學肥佬黎玩收費,轉立埸吸客?"},{"pid":"8a9bd2688c73ff1ff11bb37072961988b09f1a90","tid":1299580,"uid":60941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"009a9bc8426d347a3dc0008bd2e2d72f77c4